h the two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34642,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/05\/umar-greed-is-poverty\/","url_meta":{"origin":24638,"position":1},"title":"Umar on Greed: Greed is poverty and slavery to materialism","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Urwah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, would say in his sermons, \u201cYou know that greed is poverty and renunciation is independence. Verily, whoever renounces his desire for what people have, he will be independent of them.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd wal-Raqa\u0304\u2019iq 631 \u0639\u064e\u0646 \u0639\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28975,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/muhammad-no-better-akhlaq-adab\/","url_meta":{"origin":24638,"position":2},"title":"Aisha on Muhammad: None had better character than the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Urwah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cNo one had better character than the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. No one from his companions or his family called upon him but that he would say: I am at your service. For this reason,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9660,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/02\/generosity-mothers-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":24638,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Generosity: None more generous than Aisha and Asma","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Zubayr reported: I have not seen anyone more generous than Aisha and Asma', though their generosity was different. Aisha would gather things and after they had been collected, she would share them. As for Asma', should would not leave anything for tomorrow. Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 280 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7736,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/aisha-khadija-jealous-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24638,"position":4},"title":"Aisha on Khadijah: I was never jealous of any woman like Khadijah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Urwah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \"I never felt so jealous about any woman as I did for Khadijah. She had died three years before I married the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. I heard him mentioning her so often, and his Lord ordered\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u06